metadata.name: Living with Blue
metadata.description:
Thank you for looking.
This photo has gotten 10,000 likes and 860,000 impressions.

It looks as if the cat is looking at the ocean and thinking about something.
We can't see his expression, but that's why we can imagine so many things.

About this photo

Date: July 30, 2020
Location:  Sanagi Island, Kagawa Prefecture

I hope you will like this photo.
